And I know you're
probably tired,
you're probably hungry,

24:19.200 --> 24:21.167
but, I've got bigwig people
coming in,

24:21.233 --> 24:22.500
in the next few days,

24:22.567 --> 24:23.800
so we gotta get
that water line.

24:23.867 --> 24:25.400
-Okay.
-Get it rolling.

