walking around,

28:15.500 --> 28:17.767
and still find new things
to learn every time
I went out.

28:17.967 --> 28:19.000
And this trip has
been like that.

28:19.067 --> 28:20.533
That's what
it's all about out here.

28:21.467 --> 28:23.367
Being closer to nature.
Seeing what's going on.

28:26.433 --> 28:29.367
I'm not interested in living
