29:28.700 --> 29:31.000
And taking advantage of
the opportunities that exist.

29:31.067 --> 29:32.933
More time I spend out here,
the more I learn.

29:40.767 --> 29:41.967
CHIP: It's knowing
when to be there,

29:42.033 --> 29:43.367
what you're targeting,
and how to get it.

29:43.833 --> 29:45.267
We take the opportunity
that presents itself.

29:53.567 --> 29:55.767
Well, we prepared ourselves
for days and, uh,

29:55.833 --> 29:59.267
we did a scout trip
and now it's time for us
to go do our seal hunt.

29:59.333 --> 30:01.700
The weather has actually
calmed down, considerably,

30:01.767 --> 30:03.533
looks like a good day
for a good hunt.

30:03.600 --> 30:05.233
So, hopefully,
we'll be successful,

30:05.300 --> 30:06.600
and we'll just
take it as it comes.

